        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Such a hiding place as would have filled the heart of almost any boy with sweet delight Myles and Gascoyne found one summer afternoon.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Behind the north stable, a great, long, rambling building, thick walled, and black with age, lay an older part of the castle than that peopled by the better class of life-a cluster of great thick walls, rudely but strongly built, now the dwelling place of stable lads and hinds, swine and poultry.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "From one part of these ancient walls, and fronting an inner court of the castle, arose a tall, circular, heavy buttressed tower, considerably higher than the other buildings, and so mantled with a dense growth of aged ivy as to stand a shaft of solid green.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Myles had more than once felt an idle curiosity about this tower, and one day, as he and Gascoyne sat together, he pointed his finger and said, \"What is yon place?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"That,\" answered Gascoyne, looking over his shoulder-\"that they call Brutus Tower, for why they do say that Brutus he built it when he came hither to Britain.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Who liveth there now?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "He and his wife and those others dwell in the vaults beneath, like rabbits in any warren.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Myles stared at the tower for a while in silence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Beshrew me,\" said Gascoyne, \"but I have never thought of such a matter.\" He turned and looked at the tall crown rising into the warm sunlight with a new interest, for the thought of entering it smacked pleasantly of adventure.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"How wouldst thou set about getting within?\" said he, presently.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"So be it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "As Myles had said, the climbing from roof to roof was a matter easy enough to an active pair of lads like themselves; but when, by and by, they reached the wall of the tower itself, they found the hidden window much higher from the roof than they had judged from below-perhaps ten or twelve feet-and it was, besides, beyond the eaves and out of their reach.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Myles looked up and looked down.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Above was the bushy thickness of the ivy, the branches as thick as a woman's wrist, knotted and intertwined; below was the stone pavement of a narrow inner court between two of the stable buildings.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Methinks I can climb to yon place,\" said he.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Nay,\" quoth Myles, \"I trust not; but break or make, we get not there without trying.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "If thy neck is worth so little, mine is worth no more.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "It was indeed a perilous climb, but that special providence which guards reckless lads befriended them, as it has thousands of their kind before and since.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "So, by climbing from one knotted, clinging stem to another, they were presently seated snugly in the ivied niche in the window.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "At the bottom of the steps was a heavy oaken door, which stood ajar, hanging upon a single rusty hinge, and from the room within a dull, gray light glimmered faintly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"The ghosts!\" cried Gascoyne, in a quavering whisper, and for a moment Myles felt the chill of goose flesh creep up and down his spine.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "But the next moment he laughed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Nay,\" said he, \"they be rats.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000027_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000027_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Look at yon fellow, Francis!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "A straight beam of sunlight fell through a broken shutter like a bar of gold, and fell upon the floor in a long streak of dazzling light that illuminated the whole room with a yellow glow.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000030_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000030_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Look at yon arbalist; sure Brutus himself used such an one!\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Clouds of dust rose as they rummaged among the mouldering mass, setting them coughing and sneezing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Now and then a great gray rat would shoot out beneath their very feet, and disappear, like a sudden shadow, into some hole or cranny in the wall.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Come,\" said Myles at last, brushing the dust from his jacket, \"an we tarry here longer we will have chance to see no other sights; the sun is falling low.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000034_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000034_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "An arched stair way upon the opposite side of the room from which they had entered wound upward through the wall, the stone steps being lighted by narrow slits of windows cut through the massive masonry.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000034_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000034_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Above the room they had just left was another of the same shape and size, but with an oak floor, sagging and rising into hollows and hills, where the joist had rotted away beneath.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000034_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000034_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "It was bare and empty, and not even a rat was to be seen.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "They were in a bower of leafy green.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"This passeth wonder,\" said Gascoyne, at last breaking the silence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Entering an arched door way, the two found themselves in a beautiful little vaulted chapel, about eighteen feet long and twelve or fifteen wide.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000039_000002",
