    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000039_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000039_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "They could see the gardener, with bowed back, patiently working among the flowers in the garden, the stable boys below grooming the horses, a bevy of ladies in the privy garden playing at shuttlecock with battledoors of wood, a group of gentlemen walking up and down in front of the Earl's house.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "It was all like a puppetshow of real life, each acting unconsciously a part in the play.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150123_000040_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150123/2185_150123_000040_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "The cool wind came in through the rustling leaves and fanned their cheeks, hot with the climb up the winding stair way.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "CHAPTER eleven",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "In the intimate talks of that time Myles imparted something of his honest solidity to Gascoyne's somewhat weathercock nature, and to Myles's ruder and more uncouth character Gascoyne lent a tone of his gentler manners, learned in his pagehood service as attendant upon the Countess and her ladies.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"I do wonder,\" said Myles, quaintly, \"that thou couldst ever find the courage to bespeak a young maid, Francis.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Never did I do so, nor ever could.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Rather would I face three strong men than one young damsel.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Whereupon Gascoyne burst out laughing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Marry!\" quoth he, \"they be no such terrible things, but gentle and pleasant spoken, and soft and smooth as any cat.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"No matter for that,\" said Myles; \"I would not face one such for worlds.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "It was during the short time when, so to speak, the two owned the solitude of the Brutus Tower, that Myles told his friend of his father's outlawry and of the peril in which the family stood.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Canst thou riddle me why it is so, Myles?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "The subject was a very sore one with Myles.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000013_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000013_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "His was a brooding nature, and in the three or four weeks that passed he had meditated so much over what had been told him, that by and by it almost seemed as if a shadow of shame rested upon his father's fair fame, even though the attaint set upon him was unrighteous and unjust, as Myles knew it must be.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000013_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000013_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "He had felt angry and resentful at the Earl's neglect, and as days passed and he was not noticed in any way, his heart was at times very bitter.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "So now Gascoyne's innocent question touched a sore spot, and Myles spoke with a sharp, angry pain in his voice that made the other look quickly up.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Why may that be, Myles?\" said Gascoyne.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Gascoyne raised himself upon his elbow, and opened his eyes wide in wonder.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000017_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000017_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Why should he be afeared to befriend thee?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Myles hesitated for a moment or two; wisdom bade him remain silent upon the dangerous topic, but his heart yearned for sympathy and companionship in his trouble.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "He was cousin to the Earl of Kent, and I do remember hearing that he had a narrow escape at that time from ruin.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Then why doth he not stand forth like a man and befriend me and my father openly, even if it be to his own peril?\" said Myles, reverting stubbornly to what he had first spoken.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Gascoyne did not answer, but lay for a long while in silence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Knowest thou,\" he suddenly asked, after a while, \"who is this great enemy of whom Sir james speaketh, and who seeketh so to drive thy father to ruin?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Nay,\" said Myles, \"I know not, for my father hath never spoken of these things, and Sir james would not tell me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Not I,\" said Gascoyne.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Nay,\" said Myles, briefly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Perhaps his chief objective since the talk with Sir james following his fight in the dormitory had been successful resistance to the exactions of the head of the body of squires.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000030_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000030_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "It was the formation of a secret order, calling themselves the \"Knights of the Rose,\" their meeting place to be the chapel of the Brutus Tower, and their object to be the righting of wrongs, \"as they,\" said Myles, \"of Arthur his Round table did right wrongs.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000031_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000031_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"But, prithee, what wrongs are there to right in this place?\" quoth Gascoyne, after listening intently to the plan which Myles set forth.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000032_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000032_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Why, first of all, this,\" said Myles, clinching his fists, as he had a habit of doing when anything stirred him deeply, \"that we set those vile bachelors to their right place; and that is, that they be no longer our masters, but our fellows.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000033_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000033_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Gascoyne shook his head.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000033_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000033_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "He hated clashing and conflict above all things, and was for peace.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000033_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000033_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Why should they thus rush to thrust themselves into trouble?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000033_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000033_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "And, finally, with the hopefulness of so many of the rest of us, he advised Myles to let matters alone, and they would right themselves in time.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000035_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000035_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "As for me, I tell thee I love it not.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000036_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000036_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Why, aye,\" said Myles; \"I ask no man to do what I will not do myself.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000037_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000037_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Gascoyne shrugged his shoulders.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000037_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000037_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"So be it,\" said he.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000037_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000037_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "I for one will stand thee back while thou art taking thy raps.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Out upon it!\" cried he, his patience giving way.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Then Gascoyne yielded at once, as he always did when his friend lost his temper, and having once assented to it, entered into the scheme heart and soul.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000040_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000040_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Three other lads-one of them that tall thin squire Edmund Wilkes, before spoken of-were sounded upon the subject.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "\"Perchance,\" said he, as the five lads lay in the rustling stillness through which sounded the monotonous and ceaseless cooing of the pigeons-\"perchance there may be dwarfs and giants and dragons and enchanters and evil knights and what not even nowadays.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "Perhaps Myles, who lay silently listening to all that was said, was the only one who looked upon the scheme at all in the light of real utility, but I think that even with him the fun of the matter outweighed the serious part of the business.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000045_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000045_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "So it was that the Sacred Order of the Twenty Knights of the Rose came to be initiated.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000045_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000045_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "They appointed a code of secret passwords and countersigns which were very difficult to remember, and which were only used when they might excite the curiosity of the other and uninitiated boys by their mysterious sound.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000045_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000045_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "They elected Myles as their Grand High Commander, and held secret meetings in the ancient tower, where many mysteries were soberly enacted.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-2185_150124_000046_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/2185/150124/2185_150124_000046_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2185",
        "content": "The lucky twenty were the objects of envy of all not so fortunate as to be included in this number, and there was a marked air of secrecy about everything they did that appealed to every romantic notion of the youngsters looking on.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    }
]